<div class='mailer__content'>
  <p class='govuk-body'>Welcome <%= @user.first_name %>, to Teach primary computing!</p>
  <p class='govuk-body'>You have successfully signed up and taken your first step towards achieving your Teach primary computing certificate, awarded by BCS, The Chartered Institute for IT. We look forward to supporting you through your professional learning journey.</p>
  <p class='govuk-body'><strong>Next steps...</strong></p>
  <ol class="govuk-list govuk-list--number">
    <li>Explore your <%= link_to "personal dashboard", primary_certificate_url, class: "ncce-link" %> and discover recommended courses and activities</li>
    <li>Participate in CPD to develop your practice</li>
    <li>Engage in a range of activities to demonstrate your commitment to your professional development and your community</li>
    <li>Successfully complete the programme and receive your nationally recognised certificate</li>
  </ol>
  <p class='govuk-body'><%= link_to "Explore your dashboard", primary_certificate_url, class: 'govuk-button button' %></p>
</div>
